text: Andre Breitbarth (born April 6, 1990) is a German judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's +100 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the first round by Iurii Krakovetskii. ==References== == External links == * * * * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:German male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Germany Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games Category:European Games competitors for Germany
